1) Look at the address near the top that ends in “2025” and make sure you’re on that person’s page.  
2) Scroll gently down until you see something expressing deep gloom or sadness.  
3) Hover over that gloomy text so small symbols appear under or near it.  
4) Tap the curved shape that starts with “R” among those symbols.  
5) On the small panel that shows up, pick the option beginning with the same letter “R.”  
6) If a box appears, type any words you’d like or leave it blank.  
7) Press the bright shape (usually at the bottom) that begins with “P” to confirm and finalize.
